text.paragraph:
The recommended maximum dosage of Phentermine hydrochloride tablets, USP is 15 mg daily for patients with severe renal impairment (eGFR 15 to 29 mL/min/1.73 m2). Avoid use of Phentermine hydrochloride tablets, USP in patients with eGFR less than 15 mL/min/1.73 m2 or end-stage renal disease requiring dialysis [See Use in Specific Populations (8.6) and 

                              Clinical Pharmacology  (12.3)
                           ].

